msgctxt "68_Saejima"
msgid "(Hm? A homeless guy... Maybe I could ask him about the info dealer.)"
msgstr "(¿Mm? Un indigente. Tal vez pueda preguntarle sobre el informante...)."

msgctxt "80_Saejima"
msgid "Excuse me. Was wonderin' if I could ask ya something."
msgstr "Disculpa. Hay algo que me gustaría preguntarte..."

msgctxt "92_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "Hey!"
msgstr "¡Oye!"

msgctxt "104_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "You! Come over here!"
msgstr "¡Tú! ¡Ven aquí un momento!"

msgctxt "116_Saejima"
msgid "What happened?"
msgstr "¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "128_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "We'll talk later! Just follow me!"
msgstr "¡Date prisa!"

msgctxt "224_Saejima"
msgid "Hold yer horses, old man. Where the hell're ya headed in such a hurry?"
msgstr "Oye, espera un momento. ¿A dónde tan apurado?"

msgctxt "236_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "It's the Master! He's gonna die if we don't do something!"
msgstr "El maestro... El maestro está a punto de morir."

msgctxt "248_Saejima"
msgid "The Master?"
msgstr "¿El maestro?"

msgctxt "260_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "Yeah. He's a famous old man around these parts. Been digging a hole down in the sewers for ages now."
msgstr "Es el apodo de un anciano famoso por aquí.\\r\n"
"Ha estado cavando un agujero en las alcantarillas por años."

msgctxt "272_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "But enough chitchat! We gotta hurry!"
msgstr "¡Pero ya basta de cháchara! ¡Ven por aquí!"

msgctxt "308_Saejima"
msgid "A manhole? You sure about this?"
msgstr "¿Las alcantarillas? ¿Estás seguro?"

msgctxt "320_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "It's the fastest way! Just follow me!"
msgstr "¡Este es el atajo más rápido!\\r\n"
"¡Vamos, sígueme!"

msgctxt "332_Saejima"
msgid "Easier said than done, old man. How am I supposed to get through a manhole?"
msgstr "Más fácil decirlo que hacerlo... ¿Cómo abrimos esto?"

msgctxt "344_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "I got a special tool for opening manhole covers. But you're bigger than a buffalo, so you probably don't even need it."
msgstr "Tengo una herramienta para abrir la tapa de la alcantarilla.\\r\n"
"Y bueno, con tu fuerza, podrías abrirlo sin herramientas."

msgctxt "356_Panicked Homeless Man"
msgid "Anyways, we oughta hurry! Come on!"
msgstr "¡Como sea, date prisa! ¡Vamos!"

